{"type":null,"faqId":38985,"title":"如何使用手环检测单次运动？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">点亮手环屏幕，滑动至单次运动界面</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';layout-grid-mode:both;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084719495001.png\" style=\"width:36pt;height:58.5pt\"></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">，长按</span><img style=\"vertical-align:middle;\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084719508002.png\"><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">直到倒计时结束，手环将会检测您单次的运动数据。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line\"><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\nlayout-grid-mode:both;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084720394003.png\" style=\"width:19.5pt;height:16.5pt\"></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">：停止计时</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line\"><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\nlayout-grid-mode:both;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084719508002.png\" style=\"width:20.25pt;height:15.75pt\"></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">：继续计时</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line\"><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\nlayout-grid-mode:both;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084720742004.png\" style=\"width:20.25pt;height:14.25pt\"></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">：查看此次运动时长、运动数据及消耗的卡路里</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4295","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673017000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":40,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}